{"id":243,"date":"2024-03-23T22:50:06","date_gmt":"2024-03-23T22:50:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/?page_id=243"},"modified":"2024-11-19T11:04:56","modified_gmt":"2024-11-19T11:04:56","slug":"stage-2eme-annee","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/stage-2eme-annee\/","title":{"rendered":"stage-2eme-ann\u00e9e"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-vertical is-content-justification-stretch is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-2 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\">\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\">Stage de 2\u00e8me Ann\u00e9e<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-1 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"329\" height=\"153\" src=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-34\" srcset=\"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046.png 329w, https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/image_2024-03-22_000236046-300x140.png 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 329px) 100vw, 329px\" \/><\/figure>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-center\"><strong>Contexte du stage&nbsp;:<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Au cours de ma deuxi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de BTS, j&rsquo;ai re eu l&rsquo;opportunit\u00e9 d&rsquo;effectuer un stage au sein de la CD83, le Conseil D\u00e9partemental du Var. J&rsquo;ai \u00e9t\u00e9 int\u00e9gr\u00e9 au sein du service DSN, la Direction des Solutions Num\u00e9riques, qui constitue le service informatique du d\u00e9partement.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Pendant une p\u00e9riode de 5 semaines, j&rsquo;ai eu l&rsquo;occasion de plonger au c\u0153ur de la cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9, de comprendre ses rouages et de m&rsquo;immerger dans le monde du cyber au sein de ses locaux. Durant cette p\u00e9riode enrichissante, j&rsquo;ai eu l&rsquo;occasion de participer \u00e0 diverses missions de s\u00e9curit\u00e9 , allant de utilisation d&rsquo;un SIEM, NDR, EDR \u00e0 la sensibilisation utilisateur.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-center has-medium-font-size\">Ce stage m&rsquo;a permis d&rsquo;acqu\u00e9rir une exp\u00e9rience pratique pr\u00e9cieuse dans le domaine de la cybers\u00e9curit\u00e9 au sein d&rsquo;une structure administrative d&rsquo;importance. J&rsquo;ai pu d\u00e9velopper mes comp\u00e9tences techniques, mais aussi ma capacit\u00e9 \u00e0 m&rsquo;adapter \u00e0 diff\u00e9rents environnements de travail et \u00e0 travailler en \u00e9quipe.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-2 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-1 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-content-justification-center is-layout-flex wp-container-core-buttons-is-layout-2 wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"><\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Stage de 2\u00e8me Ann\u00e9e Contexte du stage&nbsp;: Au cours de ma deuxi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e de BTS, j&rsquo;ai re eu l&rsquo;opportunit\u00e9 d&rsquo;effectuer un stage au sein de la CD83, le Conseil D\u00e9partemental du Var. J&rsquo;ai \u00e9t\u00e9 int\u00e9gr\u00e9 au sein du service DSN, la Direction des Solutions Num\u00e9riques, qui constitue le service informatique du d\u00e9partement. Pendant une p\u00e9riode [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-243","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"blocksy_meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/243","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=243"}],"version-history":[{"count":23,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/243\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":973,"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/243\/revisions\/973"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/romain-nguyen.fr\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=243"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}